<sentence id="3">Recently , we isolated a 10-kDa thrombin binding fragment , CB3 , from the epidermal growth factor precursor homology domain ( epidermal growth factor (EGF)-like regions ) of thrombomodulin ( Kurasawa , S. , Stearns , D. J. , Jackson , K.W. , and Esmon , C.T. ( 1988 ) J. Biol. Chem. 263 , 5993-5996 ) .</sentence>
